OL,6,GViewers still watching the BBC in
OL,7,Gstandard definition on satellite will
OL,8,Gsee additional prompts reminding them
OL,9,Gto take action before the signal is
OL,10,Gturned off.
OL,12,FIt's part of the next phase of viewer
OL,13,Fsignposting in the run-up to the
OL,14,Fclosure of BBC standard definition
OL,15,Fservices on Sky and Freesat.
OL,17,FThe first phase involved replacing
OL,18,Fregional versions of BBC One with a
OL,19,Fsingle national version. In place of
OL,20,Fregional programmes, viewers already
OL,21,Fsee a red screen advising them to
OL,22,Fupgrade.
OL,3,CBBC increases on-screen messaging
OL,4,Cahead of standard definition closure
