OL,6,FMost Sky and Freesat viewers can now
OL,7,Fsee their local BBC One HD on channel
OL,8,F101, alongside the rest of the BBC
OL,9,Fchannels in HD and won't be affected
OL,10,Fby the SD switch-off.
OL,12,FFor the small number of SD-only
OL,13,Fviewers, the next phase of
OL,14,Fsignposting involves periodic
OL,15,Fmessaging popping up on BBC One
OL,16,Fduring the rest of the day. The
OL,17,Fmessage reminds viewers that only HD-
OL,18,Fenabled satellite equipment will be
OL,19,Fable to receive the BBC's services.
OL,3,CBBC increases on-screen messaging
