OL,6,FFreesat viewers are directed to
OL,7,Fhdsatelliteupgrade.co.uk to find out
OL,8,Fmore. Sky viewers are asked to
OL,9,Fcontact Sky, who are offering
OL,10,Fequipment upgrades.
OL,12,FThe additional messaging was last
OL,13,Fseen immediately after The One Show
OL,14,Fon Monday evening, broadcast over the
OL,15,Ftrailers that normally fill the gap
OL,16,Funtil the next programme.
