OL,6,FConfusingly, the messaging will also
OL,7,Fbe seen by Sky+HD and Sky Q viewers
OL,8,Fif they watch or record BBC One SD on
OL,9,Fchannel 801. They can simply switch
OL,10,Fto their local BBC One HD service on
OL,11,Fchannel 101 to get rid of the message.
OL,13,FFreeview and Virgin Media viewers are
OL,14,Fnot affected.
OL,16,FUPDATE (27th June, 7pm): since this
OL,17,Farticle was published, the BBC has
OL,18,Fconfirmed that it started inserting
OL,19,Fthe special message on 19th June.
